name: Nelson Farms
overview:
Nelson Farms provides entrepreneurial agri-business opportunities for specialty food processors, farmers, growers, and producers. Opportunities include: processing/co-packing, product development, dairy incubator, distribution, marketing and sales.

Processing: Nelson Farms is a state of the art, one stop processing facility for small scale food processors, farmers, growers, and producers. Nelson Farms is licensed by the State of NY and adheres to FDA regulations.

Distribution: Nelson Farms and Morrisville State College are establishing a state wide distribution system to assist the processor, farmer, grower, and producer in getting their products to the market place. This distribution system will provide opportunities for expansion into major markets.
